Let's get you measured up!","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_tAVJYU":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Fabi wears size L in the Bandeau Bralette.<br\/>Her bust is: 97cm and underbust : 83cm<br\/><br\/>--<br\/><br\/>The best way to establish your MUMMA MILLA size is to measure your bust and underbust measurement in cm's or inches.<\/p><p><br\/><em>Please note<\/em>: our sizing is not reflective of 'body' size, but rather 'bust' size.<br\/><\/p><p>We do recommend to size up if you are in between sizes to accomodate your changes pregnancy to postpartum.<br\/><br\/>Time to grab your tape measure!<br\/><br\/>BUST MEASUREMENT: <br\/>Standing up straight, with your arms down, take the tape measure and wrap it around your back and over the fullest part of your bust (over the nipple).<br\/><br\/>UNDERBUST MEASUREMENT:<br\/>Measure around your underbust, underneath your breasts, where the band of your bra would typically sit.<br\/><br\/>MEASURE UP A BRA YOU ARE CURRENTLY WEARING<em>:<br\/><\/em>It really helps if you can measure up a current bra you are wearing (and find comfortable!).<\/p><p>Lie the bra down, measure up the bottom band left -to-right, on the front side of the bra only. Please see our garment measurements below.<br\/><br\/>MUMMA MILLA UNDERBAND MEASUREMENTS<em>:<br\/><\/em><br\/>Small : 26-28cm<br\/>Medium: 29- 30cm<br\/>Large: 31-32cm<br\/>X-Large: 33-34cm<br\/>XX-Large: 35-36cm<\/p><p><br\/>If you need some further assistance, please email us, we are happy to help!<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"button_GyhLEA":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"PERSONAL SIZE ASSISTANCE","button_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/contact","button_style_secondary":true}}},"block_order":["heading_gN3fMw","text_tAVJYU","button_GyhLEA"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/NEW_PRODUCT_IMAGERY_JULY_202432_d62380e8-de3e-4053-9e21-a08f957898e3.jpg","height":"medium","desktop_image_width":"small","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignme